## AWS public ECR Configuration
AWS_PROFILE="default"
AWS_REGION="us-east-1"
ECR_REGISTRY="public.ecr.aws/xxxxxxx"
ECR_REPOSITORY="aws-ecr-name/my-karaoke-party"

##LOCAL DOCKER IMAGE NAME
